message.en_US: These are the weapons of Rhombus Square, the finest any human can produce!
message.pt_BR: Essas são as armas da Praça Losango, as melhores que qualquer humano pode produzir!
message.de_DE: Dies sind die Waffen Rhombus' - die besten, die je von Menschenhand gefertigt wurden!
message.zh_CN: 这里是罗姆布斯广场的武器铺，人类能生产的最好武器都在这里了！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/01]
message.ja_JP:
ここではロンバス広場産の武器を
扱っています。人間が作れる中でも
最良の装備がそろっていますよ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/01]
message.ko_KR: 인류가 생산할 수 있는 무기 중 가장 훌륭한 마름모 광장의 무기입니다!<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/01]
message.zh_TW: 這裡是羅姆布斯廣場的武器鋪，人類能生產的最好武器都在這裡了！<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/01]

message.en_US: Hmmmmm...
message.pt_BR: Hmmmmm...
message.ja_JP: うーん、うーん...<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Hmmmmm...

message.en_US: Hi?
message.pt_BR: Oi?
message.de_DE: Hi?

message.en_US: Oh!\. Sorry, I was lost in thought.
message.pt_BR: Ah!\. Desculpe, eu estava perdido nos meus pensamentos.
message.zh_CN: 哦！\.抱歉，我在想事情。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/05/14]
message.ko_KR: 오!\. 미안, 생각을 좀 하고 있었어.<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/05/14]
message.ja_JP:
ああ！\.悪いね、
考え事に没頭してたんだ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/05/14]
message.de_DE: Oh! Entschuldigung, ich war in Gedanken versunken.

message.en_US: Why?
message.pt_BR: Por que?
message.ja_JP: どうして？<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Warum?

message.en_US: Well, I'm trying to decide which weapon I should get.
message.pt_BR: Bem, estou tentando decidir qual arma eu deveria comprar.
message.zh_CN: 我在想我要换哪把武器。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ja_JP:
いやあ、どっちの武器を買おうか
決めようとしてたところでね。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Tja, ich muss mich hier für eine Waffe entscheiden.
message.zh_TW: 我在想我要換哪把武器。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]

message.en_US: Upstairs they offer the \c[3]Skirmisher\c[0], which seems pretty ideal for dealing damage close-up.
message.pt_BR: Lá em cima eles oferecem o \c[3]Skirmisher\c[0], que parece bastante ideal para combates de curta distância.
message.zh_CN: 楼上的那把\c[3]散兵\c[0]很适合近战输出。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ko_KR: 위층에서는 \c[3]교전자\c[0]를 판매하는데, 근접 대미지에 이상적인 것 같아서.<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ja_JP:
上の階では\c[3]スカーミッシャー\c[0]を
売ってるんだ。近接攻撃で
ダメージを与えたいなら
これ以上ない武器さ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Oben bieten sie den \c[3]Plänkler\c[0] an, der ideal für viel Nahkampfschaden ist.
message.zh_TW: 樓上的那把\c[3]散兵\c[0]很適合近戰輸出。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]

message.en_US: But to get it I'd still need to grind for a few more items.
message.pt_BR: Mas para conseguir isso eu ainda precisaria farmar mais alguns itens.
message.zh_CN: 但是要换的话我还得再去肝几个素材。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ko_KR: 하지만 그걸 손에 넣으려면 여전히 몇 가지 아이템이 필요해.<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ja_JP:
でも、手に入れるには、
あともうちょっとがんばって
アイテムを集めないといけなくてね。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Aber dafür müsste ich erstmal ein paar mehr Items grinden.
message.zh_TW: 但是要換的話我還得再去肝幾個素材。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]

message.en_US: The \c[3]Laser Edge\c[0], on the other hand, I could get right now.
message.pt_BR: A \c[3]Laser Edge\c[0], por outro lado, eu poderia conseguir agora mesmo.
message.zh_CN: 但是\c[3]激光刀\c[0]的话我现在就能换到。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ko_KR: 반대로 \c[3]레이저 검\c[0]은 지금 바로 가질 수 있고.<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ja_JP:
その点、\c[3]レーザーエッジ\c[0]なら
今すぐ買えるんだ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Die \c[3]Laserschneide\c[0] wiederum könnte ich mir jetzt sofort kaufen.
message.zh_TW: 但是\c[3]激光刀\c[0]的話我現在就能換到。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]

message.en_US: It's not quite as good stats-wise but still...
message.pt_BR: Os atributos dela não são muito bons, mas ainda assim...
message.zh_CN: 虽然属性不如前者就是了...<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ja_JP:
ステータス的には
若干劣るんだけど、でも...<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Die kann zwar von den Stats nicht so ganz mithalten, aber trotzdem...
message.zh_TW: 雖然屬性不如前者就是了...<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]

message.en_US: Having a Laser Edge is pretty awesome by itself, don't you think?
message.pt_BR: Ter uma Laser Edge é muito legal por si só, você não acha?
message.zh_CN: 不过激光刀也蛮帅的，对吧？<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ko_KR: 레이저 검을 가지고 있다는 것 자체로도 멋지잖아, 그렇지?<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ja_JP:
レーザーエッジはそれだけで
十分魅力的だと思うんだ。だろ？<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: So eine Laserwaffe zu haben, ist ja an sich schon ziemlich cool, oder?
message.zh_TW: 不過激光刀也蠻帥的，對吧？<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]

message.en_US: Wait!
message.pt_BR: Espera!
message.de_DE: Warte!

message.en_US: Huh?\. Two?\. What do you mean?
message.pt_BR: Hã?\. Duas\. Como assim?
message.ja_JP:
えっ？\.2？\.
どういう意味だい？<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Höh? Zwei? Was meinst du...?

message.en_US: Oh, wait!\. I can equip two weapons!
message.pt_BR: Ah, espera!\. Eu posso equipar duas armas!
message.zh_CN: 哦对！\.我能装备两把武器！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ko_KR: 아, 그래!\. 생각해 보니 두 가지 무기를 장착할 수 있지!<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ja_JP:
ああ、そうか！\.
武器は2つ装備できるってことか！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Oh, Moment! Ich kann ja zwei Waffen ausrüsten!
message.zh_TW: 哦對！\.我能裝備兩把武器！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]

message.en_US: [nods]
message.pt_BR: [acena a cabeça]
message.ja_JP: [うなずく]<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: [nickt]

message.en_US: You're right, there is no need to pick just one.
message.pt_BR: Você está certa, não tem necessidade de escolher apenas uma.
message.zh_CN: 你说的没错，何必做决定呢。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/05/14]
message.ko_KR: 네 말이 맞아. 한 가지만 정할 필요가 없었어.<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/05/14]
message.ja_JP:
君の言う通りだ、別に1つに
絞らなくてもいいんだよな。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/05/14]
message.de_DE: Du hast recht! Es gibt keinen Grund, sich zu für eine zu entscheiden!
message.zh_TW: 你說的沒錯，何必做決定呢。<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/05/14]

message.en_US: I'll get the Laser Edge now and the Skirmisher later!
message.pt_BR: Vou adquirir a Laser Edge agora e o Skirmisher mais tarde!
message.zh_CN: 我现在先换激光刀，之后再换散兵！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ko_KR: 일단 지금은 레이저 검을 사고 교전자는 나중에 사야겠다!<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ja_JP:
今回はレーザーエッジを買って、
スカーミッシャーは後で買うよ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Ich kauf mir jetzt die Laserschneide und den Plänkler dann später!
message.zh_TW: 我現在先換激光刀，之後再換散兵！<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]

message.en_US: Or...\. should I go for two Skirmishers right away?
message.pt_BR: Ou...\. devo escolher dois Skirmishers logo de cara?
message.zh_CN: 还是说...\.我应该换两把散兵呢？<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ko_KR: 아니면...\. 아예 교전자를 두 개 사버릴까?<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.ja_JP:
それとも...\.今スカーミッシャーを
2つ買ったほうがいいかな？<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]
message.de_DE: Oder...\. soll ich mir gleich zwei Plänkler holen...?
message.zh_TW: 還是說...\.我應該換兩把散兵呢？<<A<<[CHANGED 2019/04/16]

message.en_US: Welcome Seeker!
message.pt_BR: Bem-vinda Seeker!
message.zh_CN: 欢迎，探索者！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]
message.de_DE: Willkommen, Seeker!
message.ja_JP: いらっしゃい、探索者さん！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]

message.en_US: Our store now offers new \c[3]ascended gears\c[0] to all walkers of the track!
message.pt_BR: Nossa loja agora oferece novos \c[3]equipamentos ascendidos\c[0] para todos os caminhantes da trilha!
message.zh_CN: 我们店向所有寻路者出售\c[3]晋升装备\c[0]！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]
message.de_DE: Unser Geschäft bietet nun neue \c[3]Elite-Ausrüstung\c[0] für alle Wanderer des Pfades!
message.ko_KR: 저희 상점에서는 이제 고대인의 길을 걷는 모든 시커 여러분과 \c[3]각성 장비\c[0]를 거래합니다!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]
message.ja_JP:
今なら軌跡をたどる探索者さん全員に、
新しい\c[3]超越のギア\c[0]をご用意しています！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]

message.en_US: Do you want to know further details about \c[3]ascended equipment\c[0]?
message.pt_BR: Você quer saber mais detalhes sobre os \c[3]equipamentos ascendidos\c[0]?
message.zh_CN: 你想进一步了解\c[3]晋升装备\c[0]吗？<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]
message.de_DE: Möchtest du mehr über \c[3]Elite-Ausrüstung\c[0] erfahren?
message.ja_JP:
\c[3]超越の装備\c[0]についてもっと
知りたいですか？<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]

message.en_US: [nods]
message.pt_BR: [acena a cabeça]
message.de_DE: [nickt]
message.ja_JP: [うなずく]<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]

message.en_US: You recognize ascended equipment by the \c[3]orange icon\c[0] and the \i[ascended] icon in the description.
message.pt_BR: Você reconhece os equipamentos ascendidos pelo \c[3]ícone laranja\c[0] e o ícone \i[ascended] na descrição.
message.zh_CN: 晋升装备都有着\c[3]橙色图标\c[0]，以及描述中的\i[ascended]图案。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/03/05]
message.de_DE: Elite-Ausrüstung erkennst du an dem \c[3]orangenen Symbol\c[0] und dem \i[ascended]-Symbol in der Beschreibung.
message.ko_KR: 각성 장비는 \c[3]주황색 아이콘\c[0]과 설명문에 있는 \i[ascended] 아이콘이 표시됩니다.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/03/05]
message.ja_JP:
装備の説明画面を見ると、\c[3]オレンジのアイコン\c[0]と
\i[超越]のアイコンがついているところに超越の装備が表示されています。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/03/05]

message.en_US: Ascended gear will \c[3]adapt to your level\c[0]. That means its base stats will rise as your character level increases.
message.pt_BR: Os equipamentos ascendidos se \c[3]adaptarão ao seu nível\c[0]. Isso significa que atributos base do equipamento aumentarão à medida que seu nível de personagem aumentar.
message.zh_CN: 晋升装备将随着你的等级强化。这意味着角色等级提高时，装备属性也会提高。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.de_DE: Elite-Ausrüstung \c[3]passt sich deinem Level an\c[0]. Das bedeutet, dass die Grundwerte mit deinem Spielerlevel steigen.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]
message.ko_KR: 각성 장비는 \c[3]레벨에 맞춰 조정됩니다\c[0]. 캐릭터 레벨이 올라갈 때마다 각성 장비의 기본 스탯도 올라간다는 뜻이죠.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/07]
message.ja_JP: 超越のギアは\c[3]あなたのレベルに適応します\c[0]。つまり、あなたのレベルが上がると基準となるステータスも上がります。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]

message.en_US: However, note that their \c[3]modifier values\c[0] remain unchanged.
message.pt_BR: No entanto, observe que os \c[3]valores de modificação\c[0] permanecem inalterados.
message.zh_CN: 但是，它们的\c[3]修正值\c[0]不会变化。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]
message.de_DE: Beachte jedoch, dass ihre \c[3]Modifikatorwerte\c[0] unverändert bleiben.
message.ja_JP: しかし、\c[3]特殊効果の数値\c[0]は変わりませんので注意してください。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]

message.en_US: Still, \c[3]ascended equipment\c[0] should be considered the first choice for every seeker to reach their highest potential!
message.pt_BR: Ainda assim, o \c[3]equipamento ascendido\c[0] deve ser considerado a primeira escolha para que cada seeker atinja seu potencial mais alto!
message.zh_CN: 尽管如此，\c[3]晋升装备\c[0]依然是探索者发挥完全潜力的第一选择！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]
message.de_DE: Dennoch sollte \c[3]Elite-Ausrüstung\c[0] die erste Wahl für jeden Seeker sein, damit er sein größtes Potential erreichen kann!
message.ko_KR: 그래도 최고의 잠재력을 이끌어 내고 싶은 시커라면 \c[3]각성 장비\c[0]를 장착하는 게 좋을 것입니다!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]
message.ja_JP: それでも、\c[3]超越の装備\c[0]は探索者の皆さんが最初に検討すべき装備でしょう。皆さんの持てる力を存分に発揮するために最適です！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]

message.en_US: [shakes head]
message.pt_BR: [balança a cabeça]
message.de_DE: [schüttelt Kopf]
message.ja_JP: [首を振る]<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]

message.en_US: Of course!\. I'll be here should you require my help later on.
message.pt_BR: É claro!\. Estarei aqui caso você precise de minha ajuda mais tarde.
message.zh_CN: 没问题！\.如果您需要任何帮助，请随时来找我。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]
message.de_DE: In Ordnung!\. Ich bin hier, falls du später meine Hilfe brauchst.
message.ko_KR: 알겠습니다!\. 전 여기 있을 테니 도움이 필요하다면 말해 주세요.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]
message.ja_JP: わかりました！\.またご用がありましたら、こちらへどうぞ。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/02/24]
